Government of Iraq and looks forward to continued cooperation. 
</p>
<p>303. The Working Group calls upon the Government to sign and ratify the International 
Convention for the Protection of All Persons from Enforced Disappearance and accept the 
competence of the Committee under articles 31 and 32.  
