</b></p>
<p>367. The Working Group undertook a mission to Morocco from 22 to 25 June 2009 (see 
A/HRC/13/10/Add.1) followed by its eighty-eighth session, held in Rabat from 26 to 28 
June 2009. 
</p>
<p><b>  Discontinuation 
</b></p>
<p>368. Over the years, the Working Group has made numerous attempts to contact the 
source of 21 outstanding cases, but to no avail. Exceptionally, the Working Group decided, 
in accordance with its methods of work, to discontinue consideration of 21 cases. The 
Working Group believes that it cannot play a role, as no follow-up can be given to the 
cases. These cases can be reopened at any time. 
</p>
