Government. One case concerned <b>Sivakumar (Sinnathambi) Ponnampalam</b>, last seen in 
November 2008, at the Manmunaitharai Checkpoint near the Kokkadicholi ferry point, 
Manmunai, Batticaloa. It is believed that the Police Special Task Force is responsible for 
</p>
